# CODEOWNERS for ibg-controller.
#
# GitHub auto-requests these owners on any PR that touches the listed
# paths. A code owner's review is required to merge when branch
# protection is configured. Listing a single owner here isn't
# redundant: it ensures the notification fires even on tiny PRs that
# might otherwise get batched and missed.

# Default: everything.
* @code-hustler-ft3d

# Release + supply chain. These paths have outsized blast radius —
# a bad workflow edit can leak signing identity or publish a
# compromised image. Same owner today, but kept separate so future
# additions (reviewers, automation accounts) land in a focused place.
/.github/workflows/    @code-hustler-ft3d
/SECURITY.md           @code-hustler-ft3d

# Stability contracts. Changes to the public ALERT_* + /health + env
# var surfaces can silently break downstream monitors. Owner-review
# required.
/docs/OBSERVABILITY.md @code-hustler-ft3d
/docs/UPGRADING.md     @code-hustler-ft3d
/CHANGELOG.md          @code-hustler-ft3d
